Package: rbiom
Type: Package
Title: BIOM File Processing
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Daniel P.", "Smith", 
    email = "dansmith@orst.edu", 
    role  = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    Facilitates reading and working with BIOM file data, commonly 
    microbial community datasets. Includes multithreaded functions for 
    rarefying, alpha diversity, and beta diversity (e.g. UniFrac)
    calculations.
URL: https://github.com/cmmr/rbiom
BugReports: https://github.com/cmmr/rbiom/issues
License: AGPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
